name: The King Meets New Friends :)
description: This world will be beautiful and peacefuly if all beings love each other. people love their pets like dogs or cats. They really understand each other's feelings. And the most unique thing is adopting a rooster and being able to understand each other between the rooster and the people who adopt him. The Rooster is also sitting in the car, and he knows how to sit well in the car. Chickens are usually used as objects to be eaten by people, sometimes only certain people can understand their feelings. At this story,  The King Indukayam met a new friend, Mr. FluffheadChaser & The Orange Rooster. They are good friends :)
